title: Ivan Milenković
text:
Ivan Milenković (), (born 3 July 1983) is a <a href="Serbia">Serbia</a>n <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er who plays for <a href="FK%20Sin%C4%91eli%C4%87%20Ni%C5%A1">FK Sinđelić Niš</a> in the <a href="Serbian%20League%20East">Serbian League East</a>.
Born in <a href="Ni%C5%A1">Niš</a>, he started in <a href="Radni%C4%8Dki%20Ni%C5%A1">Radnički Niš</a> and played 145 games for the club. In 2007, he moved to <a href="FK%20Jagodina">FK Jagodina</a> but played only 15 games in two seasons. In 2008, he went to <a href="FK%20Mladi%20Radnik">FK Mladi Radnik</a> for a half season. In 2010, he moved to <a href="Radni%C4%8Dki%20Ni%C5%A1">Radnički Niš</a> and had three good seasons. In summer 2013 he moved to <a href="FK%20Sin%C4%91eli%C4%87%20Ni%C5%A1">FK Sinđelić Niš</a>.
